00:40:55.109 --> 00:40:56.109
&gt;&gt;Dan G: [chuckles] That's right.

00:40:56.109 --> 00:41:01.920
&gt;&gt;Ian: Because remember the java interfaces
in Android are very very easy to use compared

00:41:01.920 --> 00:41:03.140
to C and C++.

00:41:03.140 --> 00:41:05.450
There's' a lot fewer ways to shoot yourself
in the foot.

00:41:05.450 --> 00:41:08.240
You'll end up writing a lot less code.

00:41:08.240 --> 00:41:13.970
