your game play, you know, every large scale

00:41:13.970 --> 00:41:19.300
C++ project that I've worked on has its own
resource management and reflection system.

00:41:19.300 --> 00:41:23.580
Which of course is built into Dalvik and into
the java framework.

00:41:23.580 --> 00:41:27.000
So you can actually save yourself a lot of
time.

00:41:27.000 --> 00:41:29.630
Especially when you're dealing with platform
specific things.

00:41:29.630 --> 00:41:33.770
