there.

00:54:57.740 --> 00:55:01.250
And then pull those out based on the resource
id.

00:55:01.250 --> 00:55:06.410
And you'll get the different values based
on which screen size you're on.

00:55:06.410 --> 00:55:07.980
Or you know, whatever you filter it on.

00:55:07.980 --> 00:55:08.980
&gt;&gt;Dan G: Absolutely.

00:55:08.980 --> 00:55:10.440
